data.description: Charming 4-bed Cape Cod gem nestled on a dead-end street in Monitor Township. Revel in a spacious eat-in kitchen, hardwood accents, a retro fireplace, and abundant natural light through a stunning bay window. Enjoy a fenced yard, garage, and a custom built barnwood bar for entertaining. Ideal proximity to shopping and restaurants makes this home a standout!
